# NFT Minter

This applications enables users to mint tokens on the blockchain. Content and Metadatas are loaded on IPFS.
The application provides the following page structure:

- Landing page: a page where users can create a presentation for their project. This part can leverage a built in system or accept third party provided html content. Leveraging the built in system will provide users with more flexibility thanks to the dynamic nature of database systems.

- Connet-wallet page: this page provides capabilities for the application to enable user's wallet connection to the dapp.

- Success / Failure: pages which show the result of the wallet connection.

- Collection: a page
